). 
<bibRefCitation author="Walsingham, Thomas" box="[699,922,295,321]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" pagination="469 - 759" refId="ref102986" refString="Walsingham, Thomas, de Grey (Lord) (1907) Microlepidoptera. In: Sharp, D. (Ed.), Fauna Hawaiiensis. 1 (5). Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, pp. 469 - 759." type="book chapter" year="1907">Walsingham (1907)</bibRefCitation>
